OL,3,CLabourer jailed for five months for
OL,4,Cbeing abusive on flight to Gatwick
OL,6,FEdwards, 26, of Medway Road, Bow,
OL,7,FLondon, was found guilty of behaving
OL,8,Fin a threatening, abusive, insulting
OL,9,Fand disorderly manner to cabin crew,
OL,10,Fcontrary to the Air Navigation Order
OL,11,F2016, and assault.
OL,13,FAs well as the prison term, he was
OL,14,Fsentenced at Crawley Magistrates'
OL,15,FCourt to pay compensation of #2,400 to
OL,16,Fthe victims on board, a #500 fine, and
OL,17,F#675 court costs.
