OL,3,CLabourer jailed for five months for
OL,4,Cbeing abusive on flight to Gatwick
OL,6,FA Sussex Police spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Edwards was first to board the
OL,8,Faircraft, and was seen grabbing items
OL,9,Ffrom seats in an area of the aircraft
OL,10,Fhe was not travelling in.
OL,12,F"He was challenged twice about this.
OL,14,F"Then he was spoken to by a cabin crew
OL,15,Fmember after he was suspected of
OL,16,Fvaping in the toilet on board.
OL,18,F"It is illegal to use vapes as the
OL,19,Fbatteries cause a risk of fire inside
OL,20,Fthe aircraft.
