OL,3,CLabourer jailed for five months for
OL,4,Cbeing abusive on flight to Gatwick
OL,6,F"Edwards had previously been warned
OL,7,Fabout vaping on board the outbound
OL,8,Fflight from London Gatwick.
OL,10,F"After being challenged, he became
OL,11,Fabusive and swore at cabin crew
OL,12,Fworkers.
OL,14,F"He demanded a drink and was told to
OL,15,Fsit down, and a drink would be taken
OL,16,Fto him. But instead he snatched a
OL,17,Fcarton of juice and tried to walk away.
OL,19,F"During the incident he then assaulted
OL,20,Fa cabin crew worker."
