OL,3,CLabourer jailed for five months for
OL,4,Cbeing abusive on flight to Gatwick
OL,6,FDetective Constable Graham Gray, from
OL,7,FGatwick CID, said: "All abuse of cabin
OL,8,Fcrew is unacceptable, it should not be
OL,9,Fseen as just a part of their job.
OL,11,F"Edwards' behaviour was so poor that
OL,12,Fdespite being given numerous warnings,
OL,13,Fhe continued to ignore cabin crew.
OL,15,F"Indeed his behaviour was so poor that
OL,16,Fhe was given an official written
OL,17,Fwarning by the captain on board.
